{"tid":1016763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【街頭試食】德國人街頭實試香港零食 邊款一食要即刻吐？","createTime":"2019-02-11T03:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T12:22:52.000Z","uid":29627,"like":311,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea2f07b1383c3f94f0ef1badd2f0503d59494c3","tid":1016763,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"【街頭試食】德國人街頭實試香港零食 邊款一食要即刻吐？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_962e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_962e.jpg&h=6738897f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五款香港零食供德國人試吃。<br />\n<br />\nKinder朱古力、熊仔糖、二寶等等的德國零食，香港人一定不會陌生，更可謂是多年來熱門之選。但德國人又對香港零食有何看法呢？今次在街頭邀請德國人來嘗試及評價香港傳統零食：馬仔、山楂餅、話梅、齋燒鵝和杏仁餅。 <br />\n<br />\n第一樣是話梅，幾乎一面倒的劣評，部份受訪者更需要把話梅吐出來。德國人認為話梅是一種新挑戰，味道由極酸轉為極甜亦難以接受，亦不喜歡話梅中間有核。 <br />\n<br />\n第二樣是馬仔，是一致高票當選，成為德國人最愛的香港零食。德國人認為馬仔口感鬆軟，香甜的味道容易入口，貼近歐洲人口味。<br />\n<br />\n第三樣是山楂餅，部份受訪德國人認為香甜可口也吃出其水果味道。亦有德國人形容山楂餅外觀猶如香腸，味道雖有點奇怪但尚可接受，屬中規中矩的評價。<br />\n<br />\n第四樣是素燒鵝，大部份受訪者形容為意想不到的味道，並稱其香脆的口感配以甜酸鹹味是一種新奇的食物，亦無法聯想素燒鵝的主要材料。德國人解釋因為味道過於新奇不習慣，所以評價不高。<br />\n<br />\n最後是杏仁餅，德國人形容杏仁餅像下午茶點，適合配以咖啡食用。其濃郁果仁香亦接近德國人口味，頗為受歡迎的香港零食。<br />\n<br />\n雖然德國人不太喜歡部份零食，但認為只是口味不一樣，不代表不好吃，只可以說是不習慣，亦好開心嘗試到香港零食。下次想送禮給德國朋友的話，大概有概念了吧！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_61d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_61d8.jpg&h=d977b82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者在品嘗話梅後面容扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_9be6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_9be6.jpg&h=1a5d77d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者表示好開心有機會嘗試到香港零食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616472_3347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616472_3347.jpg&h=a0f710de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一受訪者在嘗試話梅後，面帶痛苦表情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616472_0b70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616472_0b70.jpg&h=5c8bae75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者認為杏仁餅像下午茶點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190211/59236778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59236778&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=17404a47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59236778&h=2e8626ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190211/59236778</a>"},{"pid":"5c2180247e80842c6b14305cf69235ae1161615b","tid":1016763,"uid":194281,"like":191,"dislike":239,"score":-48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"話梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3c5d01a0bd26cece817b775bf0e86a545eb09a","tid":1016763,"uid":83102,"like":1014,"dislike":125,"score":889,"quote":{"pid":"5c2180247e80842c6b14305cf69235ae1161615b","tid":1016763,"uid":194281,"like":191,"dislike":239,"score":-48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"話梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不知幾正"},{"pid":"ff39fd989469addbf13eb9d4b5d48a4576a8bdb7","tid":1016763,"uid":58140,"like":