3:45:11.000Z","msg":"以上五樣 得杏仁餅我係唔食<br />\n都估到五樣馬仔佢哋最buy<br />\n好甜"},{"pid":"ab1a3b2b2662d2623bff0c62198b27b96269a754","tid":1016763,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">党報毒果愈黎愈現真身，學埋支那個隻撚鬼佬以自娛自J既民瀆DNA！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僭共諜肥佬泥當年除左靠炒美帝配額發達，佐鳩奴到尾咪又係靠扮鬼佬起家！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2aff3606ebfdb8e0db3d85d34faa64f17b64874","tid":1016763,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"應該要試臭豆腐雞蛋仔夾餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268a6c2edd649133bb993df1c1381c1beea4cf06","tid":1016763,"uid":26385,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"馬仔都計香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1fc11262da58a94e966bb49201b9216837f089","tid":1016763,"uid":116471,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"3ea2f07b1383c3f94f0ef1badd2f0503d59494c3","tid":1016763,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"【街頭試食】德國人街頭實試香港零食 邊款一食要即刻吐？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_962e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_962e.jpg&h=6738897f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五款香港零食供德國人試吃。<br />\n<br />\nKinder朱古力、熊仔糖、二寶等等的德國零食，香港人一定不會陌生，更可謂是多年來熱門之選。但德國人又對香港零食有何看法呢？今次在街頭邀請德國人來嘗試及評價香港傳統零食：馬仔、山楂餅、話梅、齋燒鵝和杏仁餅。 <br />\n<br />\n第一樣是話梅，幾乎一面倒的劣評，部份受訪者更需要把話梅吐出來。德國人認為話梅是一種新挑戰，味道由極酸轉為極甜亦難以接受，亦不喜歡話梅中間有核。 <br />\n<br />\n第二樣是馬仔，是一致高票當選，成為德國人最愛的香港零食。德國人認為馬仔口感鬆軟，香甜的味道容易入口，貼近歐洲人口味。<br />\n<br />\n第三樣是山楂餅，部份受訪德國人認為香甜可口也吃出其水果味道。亦有德國人形容山楂餅外觀猶如香腸，味道雖有點奇怪但尚可接受，屬中規中矩的評價。<br />\n<br />\n第四樣是素燒鵝，大部份受訪者形容為意想不到的味道，並稱其香脆的口感配以甜酸鹹味是一種新奇的食物，亦無法聯想素燒鵝的主要材料。德國人解釋因為味道過於新奇不習慣，所以評價不高。<br />\n<br />\n最後是杏仁餅，德國人形容杏仁餅像下午茶點，適合配以咖啡食用。其濃郁果仁香亦接近德國人口味，頗為受歡迎的香港零食。<br />\n<br />\n雖然德國人不太喜歡部份零食，但認為只是口味不一樣，不代表不好吃，只可以說是不習慣，亦好開心嘗試到香港零食。下次想送禮給德國朋友的話，大概有概念了吧！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_61d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_61d8.jpg&h=d977b82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者在品嘗話梅後面容扭曲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616468_9be6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616468_9be6.jpg&h=1a5d77d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者表示好開心有機會嘗試到香港零食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616472_3347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616472_3347.jpg&h=a0f710de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一受訪者在嘗試話梅後，面帶痛苦表情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549616472_0b70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549616472_0b70.jpg&h=5c8bae75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受訪者認為杏仁餅像下午茶點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190211/59236778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59236778&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=17404a47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59236778&h=2e8626ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190211/59236778</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"歐洲唔會對馬仔陌生<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/恰克恰克\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%81%B0%E5%85%8B%E6%81%B0%E5%85%8B&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo54aGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=8a72879f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/恰克恰克</a>"},{"pid":"2be504d935d1a8642fd6f2c8a5c17442469c3d1e","tid":1016763,"uid":195570,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:48:12.000Z","msg":"香港最出名既零食係港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d8e949f1e738f9a8589c4930551f9c2df73319","tid":1016763,"uid":4957,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"杏仁餅最垃圾"},{"pid":"90d5eb2e08610fd8e0947610523eb27336b4b2e2","tid":1016763,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:49:00.000Z","msg":"話梅本身好參差"},{"pid":"c0d983abdfa15d78f7a15184ea5ee13dbd536503","tid":1016763,"uid":39470,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"一陣搵著個對glutin敏感去食齋燒鵝就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7696e91f09fc33b56db21d24c0ff62fc3670794","tid":1016763,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r